data.value: It is indeed a great pleasure to know that Bangladesh Govt. has organized a country wide program of opening website in every educational institution with an aim to easy access to internet facilities. I take pleasure to convey our heartfelt thanks to Bangladesh Govt. for arranging such program. It is no doubt a commendable step to turn our dreams of Digital Bangladesh vision 2021 into reality. It is no doubt a commendable step to turn our dreams of Digital Bangladesh vision 2021 into reality. Comilla Victoria Govt. College is an age old renowned college of Bangladesh. Website opening has added a new chapter in the history of development and progress of this college. I am conveying my greetings to the teachers, staffs and students on this occasion. Finally I would like to express my felicitation to the teachers of website committee for their services and efforts in opening website in this college. I wish every success to the program. Thanks.
